{
  "texts": [
    "Extracting insights into a mechanism of the NLP system and communicating them to the stakeholders in understandable terms.",
    "We define and elaborate on the mechanism and understandable terms aspects of the above definition in Appendix §C.",
    "These two aspects are related to the what part: what mechanism are we interpreting, what terms are we using to describe its states, and what is the scope of the explanation?",
    "Conversely, the extracting and communicating aspects are related to the how part: how are we interpreting and extracting insights and how are we presenting and communicating insights?",
    "Note that extracting is essentially the interpretability method defined in §3.1."
  ]
}